line_1: Rarely from their Inquisitive Search escapes;
line_2: Ev'n Wilye Nature, with her Protean Shapes,

line_1: Her subtile gin, that not a fly escapes!
line_2: For see where yonder sage Arachnè shapes

line_1: No flitting Elf the subtle Eye escapes,
line_2: When wanton Genii sport in antick Shapes.
